00:13:03.660 --> 00:13:06.960
I scribbled little descriptions
of things I would think of,

00:13:06.960 --> 00:13:08.790
the places where the
photos were taken,

00:13:08.790 --> 00:13:10.920
or when they were captured.

00:13:10.920 --> 00:13:13.800
With the Library
API, Legacy Republic

00:13:13.800 --> 00:13:15.900
