00:14:16.371 --> 00:14:17.970
Now, I'm going to
show you how we

00:14:17.970 --> 00:14:21.240
can create our own rich
albums using the API.

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:24.360
But before we do
that, a quick poll.

00:14:24.360 --> 00:14:26.970
How many of you out
there have a friend

00:14:26.970 --> 00:14:28.890
